dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2022. [This is a 'point' feature class representing the location where the driveway meets the road right of way. It contains the House Number and Street Name (Address). The parcel number is also included for each address 'point'.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
